line_1: By me shall now be undeceiv'd.
line_2: Those, whom your Beauties have enslav'd,
Know, one false step is ne'er retrieved,
That nor too little, nor too much believ'd,

line_1: By fire and sword the Nations undeceiv'd
line_2: Confess'd their former errors, and believ'd.
Know, one false step is ne'er retriev'd,
